    "13 This is the model's final goal, i.e., what it optimizes for.",
    "Given this final goal, it would be beneficial to the model to acquire power and resources which it can use to produce more paperclips, to prevent being shutdown (which would stop it from making more paperclips) etc.",
    "Importantly, if power-seeking is a convergent instrumental goal, then disempowering humanity is.",
    "By usurping control, AI makes sure that humans cannot shut it down or otherwise interfere with its goals.",
    "This reasoning translates to virtually every other misaligned goal."
